import React, { useState } from 'react'; import './Buy.css'; // Ensure the Buy.css file is correctly linked const Buy = () => { // State for filters const [manufacturer, setManufacturer] = useState(''); const [model, setModel] = useState(''); const [kilometers, setKilometers] = useState(''); const [year, setYear] = useState(''); const [price, setPrice] = useState(''); const [fuel, setFuel] = useState(''); const [color, setColor] = useState(''); const [features, setFeatures] = useState({ seatWarmers: false, sunroof: false, navigation: false, }); // Dummy data for car listings with more details and price rating const carListings = [ { id: 1, manufacturer: 'Volkswagen', model: 'Golf', year: 2020, kilometers: 10000, price: 20000, fuel: 'Petrol', transmission: 'Automatic', imgSrc: 'https://via.placeholder.com/300', seller: 'Volkswagen Dealership', rating: 4.8, location: 'Berlin, Germany', priceRating: 'good', // Could be "excellent", "good", "fair", "poor" }, { id: 2, manufacturer: 'Toyota', model: 'Corolla', year: 2019, kilometers: 15000, price: 18000, fuel: 'Hybrid', transmission: 'Manual', imgSrc: 'https://via.placeholder.com/300', seller: 'Toyota Main Dealer', rating: 4.5, location: 'Munich, Germany', priceRating: 'fair', }, { id: 3, manufacturer: 'BMW', model: 'X5', year: 2021, kilometers: 5000, price: 50000, fuel: 'Diesel', transmission: 'Automatic', imgSrc: 'https://via.placeholder.com/300', seller: 'BMW Specialist', rating: 4.9, location: 'Frankfurt, Germany', priceRating: 'poor', } ]; const handleFeatureChange = (feature) => { setFeatures((prevState) => ({ ...prevState, [feature]: !prevState[feature], })); }; const filteredCars = carListings.filter(car => { return ( (!manufacturer || car.manufacturer === manufacturer) && (!model || car.model === model) && (!kilometers || car.kilometers <= kilometers) && (!year || car.year === parseInt(year)) && (!price || car.price <= price) && (!fuel || car.fuel === fuel) && (!color || car.color === color) ); }); return (
